1. Install dependencies
  Fire the below command at the root of the directory structure:
  > npm install
2. To run in development mode:
  > npm start
3. To build
  > npm run build
  After successful completion of the 
  a. Then copy all all resource(css and js) in dist directory which are specified in the dist/index.html file to SharePoint.
  b. copy <people-picker>Loading...</people-picker> tag and script tags from dist/index.html file to script editor webpart. It may look similar to :

  <div>
    <people-picker>Loading...</people-picker>
  </div>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/polyfills.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/vendor.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/app.js"></script>
  
You are done.